<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>wktyr qạsyt</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- wktyr qạsyt wktyr bkyt
 wnạsy ạ̹ny ly ạ̉b wly byt
 wrjʿt lyh sẖft fy ʿynyh dmʿẗ wqạl ly ạ̹nta
 sạyb ḥḍny lyh
 ạ̉nạ qlt lh brdạn jʿạn fyk ạḥtmyt
 ạlqrạr- wḍmny ạtdfyt wsẖbʿt wạstkfyt
 wyạrytny mn zmạn ạ̉nạ knt ʿdt wjyt
 2- ạ̉nạ ạ̉kẖṭyt wʿlyk nạdyt
 sẖyl ḥmly ʿny mn ḥmwly ạ̉nạ ạnḥnyt
 ạ̉nạ bạstjyr byk yạ qdyr
 ạqblny ḥty̱ lw ạ̉kwn ʿndk ạ̉jyr
 qạl ly ạ̹nt ạbny kẖlạṣ ạ̉nạ lmạḍyk nsyt</lyrics>
